# Components Structure

The components are organized in a modular structure:

- [components/layout/](mdc:components/layout/) - Layout components including SEO and wrappers
- [components/menu/](mdc:components/menu/) - Navigation menu components
- [components/sections/](mdc:components/sections/) - Main content sections
  - [components/sections/profile/](mdc:components/sections/profile/) - Profile section components
  - [components/sections/about/](mdc:components/sections/about/) - About section components
  - [components/sections/portfolio/](mdc:components/sections/portfolio/) - Portfolio section components
  - [components/sections/contact/](mdc:components/sections/contact/) - Contact form components
  - [components/sections/blog/](mdc:components/sections/blog/) - Blog section components
- [components/switch/](mdc:components/switch/) - Toggle/switch components
- [components/pages/](mdc:components/pages/) - Page-specific components